world technology,

00:54:29.350 --> 00:54:31.920
30,000-year-old technology.

00:54:31.920 --> 00:54:39.490
But we find pictures
effortless to interpret.

00:54:39.490 --> 00:54:40.840
Actually, that's not quite true.

00:54:40.840 --> 00:54:42.381
We find them effortless
to interpret,

00:54:42.381 --> 00:54:43.910
when they come with a caption.

00:54:43.910 --> 00:54:46.530
You give a picture out of a
context, and all of a sudden,

00:54:46.530 --> 00:54:48.730
all bets are off.

00:54:48.730 --> 00:54:51.290
But with the caption
in the right context,

00:54:51.290 --> 00:54:54.000
